# Build-time-only transitive dependencies of the Gradle `checkstyle` configuration
# (Checkstyle itself, not anything bundled into the backend/web runtime images).
# Checkstyle only reads local project source files during the build; it never
# extracts untrusted archives or evaluates bean properties from external input,
# so these libraries' vulnerable code paths are not reachable here.
